Notes: bags originally labeled as bag 14, along with the bags from plot "15". 4 bags were found labeled as plot 14 - one set of strips is the true plot 14 and one set of strips should be plot 15. With support from plot composition data, we concluded that samples in this line are the true plot 14. In addition to these bags being collected by Brooklynn, senesced seed heads of verbesina occidentalis were found in a bag from this set, while not in the other set of bags. Composition data showed that the true plot 14 had more of this species present in the plot and was thus more likely to be collected as biomass.
